OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer's former director of
OL,7,Fcommunications said he was not aware
OL,8,Fof anyone in No 10 lobbying the
OL,9,FForeign Office for him to be given a
OL,10,Fsenior diplomatic role.
OL,12,FIt comes after the former top civil
OL,13,Fservant at the Foreign Office said on
OL,14,FTuesday that No 10 had pushed for Lord
OL,15,FMatthew Doyle to become an ambassador,
OL,16,Fdespite him being underqualified for
OL,17,Fsuch a role.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
