FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,FLord Doyle later resigned as Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer's communications chief last
OL,8,FMarch over his association with a
OL,9,Fconvicted paedophile.
OL,11,FSpeaking on Tuesday, he said: "I have
OL,12,Fnever sought any head of mission,
OL,13,Fambassador or any equivalent
OL,14,Fleadership-type posting.
OL,16,F"I was never aware of anyone speaking
OL,17,Fto the FCDO about such a role for me.
OL,18,FMy desire after leaving No 10 was to
OL,19,Fstay in UK politics."
