OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,FSir Olly Robbins said on Tuesday that
OL,7,FNo 10 had initiated "several
OL,8,Fdiscussions" about potentially
OL,9,F"finding a head of mission opportunity
OL,10,Ffor Matthew Doyle."
OL,12,FThe former top Foreign Office official
OL,13,Fgave evidence to MPs on Tuesday
OL,14,Fregarding his handling of Lord Peter
OL,15,FMandelson's vetting to become US
OL,16,FAmbassador.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
