OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,FHe said the proposal of making Lord
OL,7,FDoyle an ambassador made him feel
OL,8,F"quite uncomfortable", and had warned
OL,9,Fthat it would be "hard for me to
OL,10,Fpersonally defend".
OL,12,FHe also said No 10 had put him under
OL,13,F"strict instruction" not to discuss
OL,14,Fthe proposal with then-foreign
OL,15,Fsecretary David Lammy.
OL,17,FThe former senior civil servant said
OL,18,Fhe was unsure "who exactly was behind"
OL,19,Fthe suggestion or "how serious it was".
OL,26,@zD@OOUzD@fO]{D@SOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,F"I found it very hard to think how I
OL,7,Fwould explain to the office what the
OL,8,Fcredentials of Matthew were to be in
OL,9,Fan important head of mission role when
OL,10,FI was in danger of making very senior,
OL,11,Fvery experienced diplomats leave the
OL,12,Foffice," he said.
OL,14,FLord Mandelson was also asked about
OL,15,Fthe prospect of a role in Washington
OL,16,Ffor Lord Doyle, Sir Olly told MPs on
OL,17,FTuesday.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
