SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,F"I think subsequently, or maybe
OL,7,Fsimultaneously, Mandelson was asked
OL,8,Fabout whether there was a job that
OL,9,Fcould be made available in the US
OL,10,Fnetwork," he told MPs.
OL,12,F"And so I think the fact that No 10
OL,13,Fwas interested in potential diplomatic
OL,14,Foptions for Doyle was probably a bit
OL,15,Fmore broadly known than I realised at
OL,16,Fthe time."
OL,18,FLord Doyle had the whip removed after
OL,19,Fit emerged he had campaigned on behalf
OL,20,Fof a friend who had been charged with
OL,21,Fpossessing indecent images of children.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]tD@AOUxD@JO]
