OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,FHe apologised for backing then-
OL,7,Fcouncillor Sean Morton before the case
OL,8,Fagainst him had concluded, saying he
OL,9,Fbelieved the paedophile's initial
OL,10,Fassertions of innocence.
OL,12,FLord Doyle was made a peer after
OL,13,Fleaving No 10 in March 2025, but was
OL,14,Fsuspended from the House of Lords this
OL,15,FFebruary over his association with
OL,16,FMorton.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
