OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,FThe row over Lord Doyle in February
OL,7,Fheightened pressure on No 10 following
OL,8,Fthe Lord Mandelson scandal, which saw
OL,9,Fthe former US ambassador quit Labour
OL,10,Fin the wake of new revelations about
OL,11,Fhis association with Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,13,FIt led critics to raise fresh
OL,14,Fquestions about the prime minister's
OL,15,Fjudgment over his decision to nominate
OL,16,Fhis former communications chief for a
OL,17,Fpeerage last December.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
