OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,FStarmer said the former top aide "did
OL,7,Fnot give a full account" of his ties
OL,8,Fto the paedophile councillor when he
OL,9,Fwas elevated to the House of Lords.
OL,11,FAsked about the claims in the House of
OL,12,FCommons, Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,13,FCooper, who was not in post at the
OL,14,Ftime, said she was "extremely
OL,15,Fconcerned" by the suggestion, and said
OL,16,Fany appointment of Lord Doyle "would
OL,17,Fnot have been appropriate".
OL,19,FA "pattern of behaviour"
OL,26,@nD@bOUoD@XO]
