CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,FSir Ed Davey said the former civil
OL,7,Fservant's revelations about Lord Doyle
OL,8,Fshowed not just a lapse in judgment,
OL,9,Fbut a "pattern of behaviour" that was
OL,10,F"incredibly damaging" for the prime
OL,11,Fminister.
OL,13,F"Not content with appointing Peter
OL,14,FMandelson as US ambassador despite his
OL,15,Flinks to Epstein, he tried to appoint
OL,16,Fanother man with a known friendship
OL,17,Fwith a sex offender," the leader of
OL,18,Fthe Liberal Democrats said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
