PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776798669
OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,F"Every day this scandal gets worse,
OL,7,Fand it becomes clearer that the only
OL,8,Fway to draw a line under it is for
OL,9,FStarmer to go."
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Reform MP Richard Tice
OL,12,Fcalled the revelation "truly shocking
OL,13,Fevidence of secret corrupt 'jobs for
OL,14,Fboys' in Starmer's office."
OL,16,FSNP Westminster leader Stephen Flynn
OL,17,Fcalled the revelations "just
OL,18,Fextraordinary".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
