OL,3,CDisgraced Starmer aide denies claim No
OL,4,C10 pushed to get him ambassador role
OL,6,F"The idea that it is No 10 who are the
OL,7,Fvictims of others not following due
OL,8,Fprocess is, quite frankly, laughable,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
